-- Saudi Arabia Will Build Northern Border Fence, Arab News Reports
-- B y   G l e n   C a r e y
-- 2012-03-12T05:36:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-12/saudi-arabia-will-build-northern-border-fence-arab-news-reports.html
Saudi Arabia  will build an 890-
kilometer (553-mile) fence along its northern border to prevent
smuggling and infiltration,  Arab News  reported, citing Border
Guards spokesman Colonel Salem Al-Sulami. The kingdom is
bordered in the north by Iraq and Jordan.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Glen Carey in Dubai at 
 gcarey8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at   barden@bloomberg.net . 